{"tid":795276,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搭程車都可以見到令人又愛又恨嘅香港","createTime":"2018-08-27T01:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T02:03:02.000Z","uid":83025,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"deab2bf12989fc8ce831d09435054717f51fbaa9","tid":795276,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:37:45.000Z","msg":"話說今朝返工<br />\n八點左右人流最多就梗係睇盡人間百態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先搭地鐵由九龍去港島，其實係有啲難過，<br />\n硬係覺得四周聽到嘅都係普通話居多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身已經夠迫啦，扶手果陣又有個大陸細路郁黎郁去<br />\n個呀媽又係唔多理果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽住前前後後都有人講緊普通話，<br />\n有一刻心諗：我究竟喺香港定大陸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但落完地鐵 (大學站)，居然又比我睇多好多溫暖人心嘅畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先喺𨋢，有個香港媽媽帶住兩個上幼稚園嘅女，佢好細心咁同啲女講叫佢地小心唔好比個書包撞到人，要有禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲小朋友都好乖好聽話，見到入𨋢嘅嫲嫲又好開心咁打招呼，個畫面好溫馨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後搭巴士，有個鬼佬見到一個盲人上車，就好主動走過去拖住佢坐低，仲用好純正嘅廣東話話佢知有位。果下睇到有啲感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下個站仲有個呀太讓位比個行動不便嘅男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實香港人真係幾好<br />\n我覺得每個人多啲留意身邊有需要嘅人，個世界會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係見到越黎越多冇教養嘅大陸人落黎整亂呢個地方，覺得有啲心灰意冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3116ef5bbe3236fde5e550c86b667577d156cde9","tid":795276,"uid":113164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:43:32.000Z","msg":"其實好多香港人都仲好有禮貌/教養 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439e89b4b989b2b5026af18b6390f17c7ecfb3e3","tid":795276,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:45:38.000Z","msg":"雙面人黎嫁啫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係細路面前梗係扮有家教，自己一個出到街咪又係典型r水港豬。"},{"pid":"208d469e7e60a88a0ff28eaf75ca595f4b24522f","tid":795276,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"439e89b4b989b2b5026af18b6390f17c7ecfb3e3","tid":795276,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:45:38.000Z","msg":"雙面人黎嫁啫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係細路面前梗係扮有家教，自己一個出到街咪又係典型r水港豬。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:47:24.000Z","msg":"咁又唔可以以偏概全嘅，一啲啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對香港人仲有少少信心"},{"pid":"cc42b80b589b0f6eb949f8b81afaf68035a6715a","tid":795276,"uid":78873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"439e89b4b989b2b5026af18b6390f17c7ecfb3e3","tid":795276,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:45:38.000Z","msg":"雙面人黎嫁啫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係細路面前梗係扮有家教，自己一個出到街咪又係典型r水港豬。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:49:50.000Z","msg":"岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個都係 你個野壞咗喎 果啲fd, 政治既野唔理架喎 etc."},{"pid":"7e8b3748eb7dfc38d44eefa8f6cc1bcfd0622730","tid":795276,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"我試過有一次放工點勁多人撘車係金鐘，應該個個都係放工既香港人，雖然好多人等左幾班，個個都默默排隊上車好有規矩，等左十五分鐘居然冇人嘈。"},{"pid":"0d60860d5a854ebfedfdd2f2e8a5c8f15f2aaea1","tid":795276,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e8b3748eb7dfc38d44eefa8f6cc1bcfd0622730","tid":795276,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"我試過有一次放工點勁多人撘車係金鐘，應該個個都係放工既香港人，雖然好多人等左幾班，個個都默默排隊上車好有規矩，等左十五分鐘居然冇人嘈。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T02:01:12.000Z","msg":"我都試過，仲要成個月台都係好靜，一粒聲都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5e8d59abb